{"tid":2396683,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–大自然界的欺詐高手","createTime":"2021-02-05T20:34:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T00:41:34.000Z","uid":38861,"like":51,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d9ae5e9cbad9a0089daf59ad0fdda8632e4feafb","tid":2396683,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T20:34:57.000Z","msg":"全球已知約有30萬種開花植物品種，而菌類品種則約有3百萬之多。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d69j1yA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd69j1yA.jpg&h=62ae1aca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n論說兩者之間的關係，很多時候都是菌類寄生在開花植物上，對植物做成各種的破壞。<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）如圖中所見，某些菌類不但寄生在植物頂部，更會發展出與原本植物幾可亂真的狀態，藉此吸引昆蟲前來幫忙往外播種。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LANd50j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLANd50j.png&h=fbeb26bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）除視覺相似外，研究(Ref1)更發現菌類會施展氣味攻勢，釋發出至少多達10種化學物，其中一種為2-ethylhexanol，正是主角開花植物會釋放的化學物。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FmSmvr3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFmSmvr3.png&h=2662a370&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而另外的化學物例如&alpha;-farnesene, nerolidol, and &beta;-farnesene等，均被證實帶有吸引各類蜜蜂前來「採蜜」的功效。<br />\n<br />\n把對手的外貌及氣味參照得維肖維妙，一切也是為了讓自己的後代得以散播開去。大自然的一事一物，實在是絕對不能看少。<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=07E5ZYF2Wb2hLaoCEA3MjOu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=15eb3e84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=07E5ZYF2Wb2hLaoCEA3MjOu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=51ef7ffd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n基於WhatsApp/Facebook等問題，IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1087184520301572?via%3Dihub\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS1087184520301572%3Fvia%253Dihub&d=07E5ZYF2Wb2hLaoCEA3MjOu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=4090951b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1087184520301572?via%3Dihub</a>"},{"pid":"36913b5eafbb5b86e69fa107bc2e81c7c585b3bb","tid":2396683,"uid":142247,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T20:47:49.000Z","msg":"成日覺得菌類好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f302b67c20975d26ecf7e6913b356dbb9cf9ec7","tid":2396683,"uid":38861,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"36913b5eafbb5b86e69fa107bc2e81c7c585b3bb","tid":2396683,"uid":142247,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T20:47:49.000Z","msg":"成日覺得菌類好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T20:56:22.000Z","msg":"能夠做到咁真係好痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d12a95759aba2050f02bc8e10aa1abce668bb056","tid":2396683,"uid":142247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3f302b67c20975d26ecf7